title: No. 9 Duke Welcomes No. 12 Virginia, Virginia Tech - Duke University - GoDuke.com
content: No. 9 Duke Welcomes No. 12 Virginia, Virginia Tech - Duke University  GoDuke.com
description: DURHAM – The No. 9 Duke women's tennis team continues ACC action as the Blue Devils welcome 12th-ranked Virginia and Virginia Tech to Durham to open a five-match homestand.
